<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح - <span class="c2">((الظلال)</span>) <span class="c2">(٨٤٢)</span>، ومضى نحوه <span class="c2">(١٨٢)</span>: ق.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>